    <string name="sample_document_title">PageTurner Service Note</string>
    <string name="sample_document_body">PageTurner is a quiet reader for e-ink devices.\n\nIt treats translation as a reading companion instead of a bot. Text is translated in paragraph batches, paced by the reader\'s speed, and saved for offline use.\n\nWhen network is available, the same pipeline can prefetch translated pages in advance. Later, the viewer can load the saved translation without another API request.\n\nThe first version focuses on the shape of the service: stable document chunks, cache keys, paced requests, and a simple viewer that can prove the flow.</string>
